{"tid":429914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有線新聞刺針] 山景邨學校機構難用公用空間","createTime":"2017-10-09T11:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T15:33:49.000Z","uid":43189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3395be0e743fa5775d7594d6678ff04cd366a9","tid":429914,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:02:08.000Z","msg":"屯門山景邨因為早前一對母子被發現倒斃屋內，成為新聞焦點。原來這條屋邨一直規矩多多，學校想借球場上堂，義工想上門做家訪，都要向法團事先申請，而且困難重重。「新聞刺針」嘗試去找法團主席問個究竟，結果怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n【全民皆針】報料方式<br />\nWhatsApp/Telegram：91464510<br />\nInstagram：newslancet<br />\nFacebook Inbox：新聞刺針<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=814542035385506&amp;id=153300521509664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D814542035385506%26id%3D153300521509664&d=hAoLjnH3VPVtREvRwMsKRP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1b84c09c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=814542035385506&amp;id=153300521509664</a><br />\n<br />\n啲租置計劃屋邨原來房屋署係廢既，公用空間都唔去管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdd1f81f89a9a91ae1c022e7295a829388edab6","tid":429914,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"球場係唔係條邨？<br />\n如果係條邨 向法團申請好正常"},{"pid":"77e44549c2bacd8f301ee51ad3929cd0b93111d8","tid":429914,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"新聞刺針不嬲正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cbbbd87cbf12229abda6c3e41896b6e1326838","tid":429914,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"留名睇"},{"pid":"be5f40a641f2038240639a6383d2d044425e8873","tid":429914,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>球場係唔係條邨？<br />\n如果係條邨 向法團申請好正常</blockquote><br />\n球場係同條邨共用，學校無球場<br />\n問題係學校有咁多班無可能次次都向法團申請<br />\n<br />\n所以當初政府話賣就賣係衍生好多問題出嚟"},{"pid":"57819d21ab8fe8a0388929e99656313ecfba056e","tid":429914,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>球場係唔係條邨？<br />\n如果係條邨 向法團申請好正常</blockquote><br />\n球場係同條邨共用，學校無球場<br />\n問題係學校有咁多班無可能次次都向法團申請<br />\n<br />\n所以當初政府話賣就賣係衍生好多問題出嚟</blockquote><br />\n睇條片+其他安老院院長反映,<br />\n都睇到個法團主席幾閪。<br />\n派十幾個保安趕記者走。<br />\n唔知仲如為D保安係佢私人保鑣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36142d34669999eade5c9f2695dd8166715dc98","tid":429914,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"個法團主席出街似皇帝出巡"},{"pid":"c2b8bfe8b97f15ed80c26e25661c0cfe02b83154","tid":429914,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:21:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個法團主席出街似皇帝出巡</blockquote><br />\n香港啲法團好多土皇帝"},{"pid":"733010fa95b6e747d6adf1f188e9c3a8ba1a6f10","tid":429914,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"總之屯門「X景邨」之類原出租公屋一帶，都出現呢類管理衝突怪現象 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f0d8556d49c98eaeb49caa76771d91798caed9","tid":429914,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個法團主席出街似皇帝出巡</blockquote><br />\n香港啲法團好多土皇帝</blockquote><br />\n條邨搞得好土皇帝唔緊要<br />\n呢條山景邨問題係似大城市入面有山番區咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}